itedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T10:49:33.000Z","msg":"辯方在庭上播放當日片段，顯示被告曾出言指責一名在場男子滋擾兩名女學生，被告與男子發生口角，男子事後離去。辯方向鄧指出，被告曾向現場警員埋怨「搞&times;錯呀，睇&times;住個阿叔頭先搞學生妹又唔&times;理」，有警員稱「阿Sir做嘢唔&times;使你教」，另一名警員則出言威嚇「拉&times;佢」，被告隨即被警員按下制服，鄧不同意。<br />\n<br />\n辯方再向鄧指出，事實為其他在場人士罵警「助紂為虐」，鄧誤認為是被告罵警，直指鄧作供不盡不實。鄧全數否認。審訊明天繼續。<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210217/2BHNH432PBCPTDVOWPCWUQF2RA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210217%2F2BHNH432PBCPTDVOWPCWUQF2RA%2F&d=bV20Ktv%2Bt3m81RcJrVEN24dddMXd0Scb%2F0m37zAf7q8%3D&h=1b4d873d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210217%2F2BHNH432PBCPTDVOWPCWUQF2RA%2F&h=691cc2f3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210217/2BHNH432PBCPTDVOWPCWUQF2RA/</a>"},{"pid":"8c5e52d686a10be17e18cabaee89560541f96ec4","tid":2411441,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T11:14:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f7c3ade16248a3ff310ac0ee1a2b0ae005de58e","tid":2411441,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T12:03:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3799cb66cae82d890bbec7d28bd7ca9afbec368b","tid":2411441,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T12:43:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}